name: Alto saxophone owned and played by Charlie Parker
description:
Alto saxophone owned and played by Charlie Parker. The saxophone consists of seven parts: a body, neck, two [2] mouthpieces, two [2] ligatures and a reed.

Owned by Charlie Parker, American, 1920 - 1955

Medium: brass (alloy), silver, mother of pearl, cork (bark)

On View
NMAAHC (1400 Constitution Ave NW), National Mall Location, Culture/Fourth Floor, 4 053
